Reasoning: The paper discusses incremental natural language processing, which is a subfield of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses different strategies and approaches for dealing with incremental processing, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as well as evaluating the effectiveness of these strategies (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the benefits of incremental processing for human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and the challenges of evaluating incremental systems (cs.SD).
